t think I need to establish your date and place of birth, because your CV gives it. 27th May, 1935, Barnsley in South Yorkshire. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
