\par Anne:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 Would you say that that was a little bit like a sort of stable that Everett Hughe
s had going in the forties where he was studying different occupations, whether it be medicine or boxers, with the same kind of principle of a sort of separate studies of a group with similar kind of themes? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
