Which is your discussions, or even arguments about, and with qualitative researchers more recently, in the last 15 years, discussions of the failings of qualitative work. Is that something we can pick up a bit? Do you think they\rquote ll link? }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
