\par John:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 No. Her mother did a General 
Degree at the University of Wales, I think in later life. And then she had an elder sister who went to university in Cardiff, qualified as a doctor. So that was her family, and her father was Headmaster of the Grammar School she went to. And then he becam
e Warden of Coleg Harlech, which is the equivalent to Ruskin in Wales. Yes. So she moved from South Wales, near Neath, where she grew up, and I think when she was a teenager, they moved up to North Wales. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
