Oh yes! I was the first person, in my immediate family, to have secondary education. There were one or two distant cousins, I think, at least one, possibly two, who\rquote d - as they used to say in those days, \'93been to college\'94
 - and these were women who had been to teacher training colleges and become non-graduate primary school teachers. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
