\par John:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 Neither, unfortunately. What I\rquote ve got at the moment is nearly finished. It\rquote 
s this ridiculous length of about 15 or 16,000 words \endash  double article length \endash  and these days, it\rquote s almost impossible to publish anything like that. So what I\rquote m going to do - I\rquote 
ll probably finish it in the next month or so - I\rquote m going to show it to a few colleagues, and decide whether it would be better to try and compress it into one article, or expand it into a book. But expanding it into a book at my age is not \'85
 I don\rquote t know (LAUGHS) Anyway, I\rquote ll see! }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
