\par Anne:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 Let\rquote s pick up Paul\rquote s interview guide. A section called \'93Pioneering Research\'94
. I hope you will accept the designation \'93pioneering\'94. I mean, actually, I\rquote m not asking you to blow your own trumpet unduly except to say what do you think is the
 research which is your main contribution - where you broke new ground, or pioneered, or \'85 or moved things in a novel direction. Perhaps you could talk about what you think comes, you know, matches any of those descriptions. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
\ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
