\par Anne:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
You actually mentioned the second quick question I was going to ask, and that was funding... I was wondering what funding you got, and how difficult it was to get. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
