\par Anne:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 (LAUGHS) And it also says, \'93Children. Ideals of parenting, hopes and ambitions for children\'94, do you want to talk about that? }{
