\par Anne:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 Is there anything that\rquote s been a major disappointment, professionally? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
