\par Anne:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 Yeah, of course they\rquote d recognise it. Well, that was the one question that I left last time, thinking, \'93I wish I\rquote 
d asked you!\'94 So thank you for that. Now, if we pick up Paul\rquote s queries. He asks whether you had any teachers at your primary school or grammar school who were significantly supportive or influential. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
