s actually quite significant, because I was listening, and expecting you to say \'93similarities\'94, and then when you said \'93commonalities\'94, that actually implied something - I\rquote m going to be cautious in using this word, \'93
that much more universal\'94. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
