How were you in Ireland?\'94 I think he means how did you get there, or why were you there? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
