 whether you can explain, for a non-statistician, the difference between causal path analysis, and log-linear modelling. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
