\par Anne:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 That\rquote s great! Thank you. Well, let\rquote 
s see what Paul makes of it. Oh, this is this question which we talked about, perhaps obliquely. I think Paul is wanting to press you on the question. Following the decision not to include women, which I think, actually, was a sort of funding decision, wa
sn\rquote t it, not an intellectual decision. But he then asks, \'93Have you included women in your subsequent social mobility studies?\'94 And I suppose he\rquote s then saying, if you have, has that affected conclusions from earlier studies? }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
