\par Anne:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 How very interesting! Well, you\rquote ve tackled this beautifully! Thank you. Now, what does Paul ask? He says, \'93
in your earlier research for the Affluent Worker project, you tried to combine quantitative and qualitative data. Do you see any role for combining such forms of data in future social research?\'94 }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 
