\par Anne:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10491433\charrsid10491433 Well, Dick Hobbs\rquote s work, I don\rquote t know Dick very well, and I don\rquote t know what he\rquote 
s done recently, but talking to me, I think I\rquote m right in saying, he would indicate that it wasn\rquote t always very safe. The last time I was in touch with him was when the last of the two Kray twins, well, the second of the two Kray twins died. }
